  "title": "Warehouse Assistant (East/West, Alt Sat Half Day)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Receive, pick, and pack goods, as well as load and unload cargo.</li><li>Stuff and un-stuff containers while ensuring proper handling of materials.</li><li>Store materials with appropriate tagging and maintain accurate tracking records.</li><li>Ensure proper housekeeping and organization in the warehouse.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Able to perform manual work and handle warehouse operations efficiently.</li><li>Attention to detail for accurate stock labelling and inventory tracking.</li><li>Committed to follow safety guidelines and maintain cleanliness.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
